::Killfest/Scyther/Incarcinator::

Killfest looks after the retreating Decepticons.

"Well, our alliance with them is over apparently," he says, looking at 
Greven's corpse. He walks over and picks it up.

"Lets get to base," he tells the other Predacon leaders, flying off 
toward the Blackfortress.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Scyther follows Killfest, still cloaked.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Seeing Killfest flying back toward base, Incarcinator slowly begins to 
follow him.
